 <p>Use this form to create a new medical department or specialty unit in the hospital. Specility help organize doctors and services.</p>
                <form action="/admin/save_specility" method="post" >
                <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 20px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 20px;">Specility Creation Form</h3>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">Speciality Name</label>
                        <input type="text" style="width: 100%; max-width: 500px; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px;" placeholder="Cardiology, Emergency Medicine, etc." name="spe_name">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">Specility IMG </label>
                        <input type="text" style="width: 100%; max-width: 500px; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px;" placeholder="Paste link here" name="icon">
                        
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">Short Description</label>
                        <textarea style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; height: 90px;" placeholder=" Describe inshort" name="short_description"></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                        <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;">About Specility</label>
                        <textarea style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; height: 120px;" placeholder="Describe the department's purpose, services, and specialties... in breaf" name="about_specility"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    
                  
                    
                    <button style="background-color: #2ecc71; color: white; border: none; padding: 14px 30px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px;" >
                        <i class="fas fa-clinic-medical" style="margin-right: 10px;"></i> Create Specility
                    </button>
                    
                </div>

                </form>

